{"id":150783,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/05/德国前总统克勒不后悔辞职决定/","date":"2011-05-08T11:30:16Z","modified":"2011-05-08T11:30:16Z","title":"德国前总统克勒不后悔辞职决定","content":"<div>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">柏林</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">前联邦德国总统克勒仍认为，一年前他出人意料辞职是正确的。克勒对今天（</span><span>5</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">月</span><span>8</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">日）一期的《星期日图片报》说，“我从未后悔过自己的这一决定”。现年</span><span>63</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">岁的基民盟籍人士克勒同时承认，辞职后，他仍长期在思考相关事宜。</span><span>2010</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">年</span><span>5</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">月</span><span>31</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">日，克勒宣布辞职，成为德国历史上首位主动辞职的在任总统。辞职的背景是克勒有关德国国防军在阿富汗使命的表态。克勒当时曾表示，德国在阿富汗的军事使命也涉及包括经济利益在内的德国国家利益。这一表态在国内引起强烈反响和争议。尤其是反对派阵营批评总统是在间接宣扬“炮舰政策”。</span></p>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGltcHJlc3Npb24iLCAicHJvcGVydGllcyI6IHsidG9rZW4iOiAiYTRhNDYwYTM5MDRlZWU4ZmY1ZTAyNGVhNGJkZTdhYzIifX0=&#038;ip=1&#038;img=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" /><img src=\"http://pixel.quantserve.com/pixel/p-89EKCgBk8MZdE.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" /><a href=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGNsaWNrIiwgInByb3BlcnRpZXMiOiB7InRva2VuIjogImE0YTQ2MGEzOTA0ZWVlOGZmNWUwMjRlYTRiZGU3YWMyIn19&#038;ip=1&#038;redirect=http://talkita.com/wrap?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw-world.de%2Fdw%2Farticle%2F0%2C%2C15059165%2C00.html%3Fmaca%3Dchi-rss-chi-all-1127-rdf&#038;title=%E5%BE%B7%E5%9B%BD%E5%89%8D%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%9F%E5%85%8B%E5%8B%92%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8E%E6%82%94%E8%BE%9E%E8%81%8C%E5%86%B3%E5%AE%9A\">Chat about this story w/ Talkita</a></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<inpu